--- !u!114 &986969958
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 986969956}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: bd5d36071c7f148469238a0fcb5284df, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textComponent: {fileID: 250996690}
  lines:
  - Long ago in a big rainforest lived Sang Kancil. Sang Kancil was feeling thirsty
    today, so he decided to walk through the forest to drink from the river.
  - When he arrived, he sees a red guava tree filled with big delicious fruit. But
    there's just one problem, the tree is on the other side of the river.
  - As he was thinking, Sang Kancil then suddenly feels a sharp pain on his foot.
    When looks down, he sees that Sang Buayas teeth are biting down on his foot .
  - '"HAHA! Looks like you will be my lunch for today." exclaims Sang Buaya. '
  - Sang Kancil was frightened, he had to come up with a plan to get out of this.
  - 'So with quick thinking, Sang Kancil responded "I''ve come to tell you some good
    news" Sang Buaya asks. "What is it? Is it better than you being my lunch?" '
  - '"Much better. The king is planning on having a feast for all the animals in
    the forest including the crocodiles." Sang Kancil states. "A feast?" says Sang
    Buaya. '
  - '"Yes. He shall be serving the finest of foods that the forest can provide" Sang
    Kancil says, confidently. "How exciting!" Sang Buaya drools. '
  - '"However, the king assigned me to count how many are coming. Can you help me?"
    Sang Kancil asks.'
  - '"No problem, I will gather all the crocodiles so you can count them." says Sang
    Buaya.'
  - '"Why, thank you Sang Buaya~" Sang Kancil says as he grins.'
  - Sang Buaya then got busy gathering all the other crocodiles to the river. After
    a few moments pass, Sang Buaya manages to gather all the crocodiles
  - '"Alright, now then Sang Kancil you can go ahead and count them now." says Sang
    Buaya "Will do!" says Sang Kancil'
  - After jumping on the crocodiles to reach the other side of the river, Sang Kancil
    jumps onto the bank.
  - Then, Sang Kancil runs to the guava tree and snacks on a couple of the fruits
    until he's full
  - '"Huh? Where are you going, Sang Kancil?" asks Sang Buaya. "You haven''t finished
    counting all of us yet."'
  - Sang Kancil then laughs "Hahaha! Haven't you figured it out, already? There is
    no feast, I just tricked you to get across the river."
  - Sang Kancil then runs back into the forest before the crocodiles try to chase
    him.
  - 
  textSpeed: 0.05
