  m_text: 'How to play:


    1. Swipe your Finger across the screen to move


    2.
    Jump on a crocodile or lilypad to Avoid falling into the water or else you will
    lose a life


    3. Avoid standing on lilypads for too long


    4. if you
    lose all your lives, you lose


    5. Reach the red guava tree to win the level'
